      • setReturnCompleteCount

        IQuery<T> setReturnCompleteCount(boolean returnCompleteCount)

      • setNativeCommand

        void setNativeCommand(java.lang.Object command)
        Add a command, which is a database specific object like an sql string or a JsonObject for mongo. If a native command is added, other parameters are ignored on execution. When the IQuery is executed later, then the native command is executed and the result is transformed into the POJOs of the defined mapper class
        Parameters:
        command - the command to be executed
